data.description: Welcome home to 407 Brown Ave!  This home features  3 bedrooms (and finished attic space which could be used as a 4th bedroom), 1.5 bathrooms, large kitchen, nice size rooms, hardwood floors on main level and newer carpet upstairs.  The nice size yard is fenced in and welcomes 3 off street parking spaces.  Close to schools, shopping, dinning, and much more!
